        <item>
            <title>Rubien 0.1.6</title>
            <description><![CDATA[• iCloud sync now pulls remote changes automatically — on launch, on focus,
  and periodically while open.
• Fixed a sync stall where a cross-device tag conflict could halt
  all syncing; conflicts now self-resolve.
• Deleting an in-use tag or select option now asks
  first; unused ones delete in one click.
• Fixed an option-picker height glitch after canceling
  a delete.]]></description>
