        <item>
            <title>Rubien 0.1.7</title>
            <description><![CDATA[• Reader: refreshed liquid-glass annotation popovers and a cleaner, transparent note
  editor
• Detail view: edit title, authors, abstract, and notes inline
• MCP server now on npm: connect Claude
  to your library with  npx -y rubien-mcp-server
• Prebuilt Linux rubien-cli now ships with releases (signed,
  with in-place self-update)]]></description>
