        <item>
            <title>Rubien 0.1.8</title>
            <description><![CDATA[• Appearance — choose Light, Dark, or System in Settings → General. Applies across the
  whole app, including reader windows.
• View icons — pick a custom icon for each view when creating or editing
  it.
• BibTeX import — {capitalization-protection} braces are now stripped from titles and fields.]]></description>
