            <title>Rubien 0.1.10</title>
            <description><![CDATA[• Fix a crash that could occur during iCloud sync
• Search now ranks results by relevance (best match first), not just by date added
• Re-adding a paper already in your library now confirms it and jumps to it, instead of silently doing nothing]]></description>
