        <item>
            <title>Rubien 0.1.11</title>
            <description><![CDATA[• New flat, left-aligned toolbar (Properties, Search, Add paper, Add website, Add manually, Import PDF).
• Reference details now open in a floating, resizable glass panel — toggle it with the Details button.
• The "Update ready" indicator now appears automatically and is easier to spot.
• Web clips: more reliable extraction on single-page-app sites, plus correct in-page (#fragment) link handling.]]></description>
