        <item>
            <title>Rubien 0.1.12</title>
            <description><![CDATA[UI polish: subtle hover highlights on table rows, the view chrome bar (Add filter / Sort / Group / Wrap), and the Properties menu make controls read as interactive. "Add manually" now lives in the import menu, and the stray keyboard focus ring that auto-highlighted the first control when a popover or sheet opened is gone.

Reliability: a database busy-timeout keeps concurrent writes from being silently dropped under load.]]></description>
